section.section:
If appropriate, the plan required in the report under paragraph (2) of this subsection shall include recommended:
mental health treatment, including providers of care;
vocational, rehabilitative, or support services;
housing;
case management services;
alcohol or substance abuse treatment; and
other clinical services.

If the report required under paragraph (2) of this subsection recommends community placement for the defendant, the report shall include:
the location of the recommended community placement;
the names and addresses of the recommended service providers;
a statement indicating if the service provider is willing and able to serve the defendant; and
if available, the date of placement or service for the defendant.
